Use Graphics.drawImage() method:
g.drawImage(myImage, x, y, ImageObserver);
Typically use ImageIO.read() to load images.

Use Graphics2D scaling:
Graphics2D g2d = (Graphics2D)g;
g2d.scale(2.0, 2.0); // For 2x scaling

Set component opaque property to false:
setOpaque(false);
Ensure parent container properly paints background.

